{"tid":346444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮泄密頻頻！特朗普致電墨西哥總統談築牆對話流出　共和黨汗顏","createTime":"2017-08-04T03:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T23:36:30.000Z","uid":9542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3156578e4629dffd89c5596134c27bda22c3f8","tid":346444,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"根據《華郵》公開的錄音，特朗普在今年1月27日一則通話中，責備涅托公開表達對圍牆的不滿。「你不能跟傳媒這樣說。」特朗普說。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在去年總統大選時承諾會在美國南方邊境興建圍牆，並指明要讓墨西哥支付相關費用。但這份錄音顯示特朗普承認資金應「從其他渠道而來」，更很有信心地說「錢的問題總能解決」。<br />\n<br />\n「如果你說墨西哥不會支付，那麼我就不再想見你們了，因為我受不了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Donald Trump suggested his demand for payment for a border wall with Mexico was merely a political ploy,</span> and told Mexico&rsquo;s president his refusal to pay should not be mentioned in public."},{"pid":"56d075f96ad8985c668bfc83f99086e8e2f4b275","tid":346444,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"汗顏點解"},{"pid":"06005797d72969e24b8214f8f267a7da7d85c7e2","tid":346444,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:06:40.000Z","msg":"The Washington Post 有Full Transcript<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/graphics/2017/politics/australia-mexico-transcripts/?hpid=hp_rhp-top-table-main_trumpcalls-915a-flipper%3Ahomepage%2Fstory&amp;utm_term=.cf39b456a4aa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fgraphics%2F2017%2Fpolitics%2Faustralia-mexico-transcripts%2F%3Fhpid%3Dhp_rhp-top-table-main_trumpcalls-915a-flipper%253Ahomepage%252Fstory%26utm_term%3D.cf39b456a4aa&d=GOD2VbLj2pT0IRhDxHdDR57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=26915141\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/graphics/2017/politics/australia-mexico-transcripts/?hpid=hp_rhp-top-table-main_trumpcalls-915a-flipper%3Ahomepage%2Fstory&amp;utm_term=.cf39b456a4aa</a>"},{"pid":"d59a99abcbddeb2826ad68815ca270aae1f3746e","tid":346444,"u